## Individual Setup Scripts

### RAG Servers (db2-docs, visual-cobol-docs, Dedge-code)

```powershell
# Setup
pwsh.exe -NoProfile -File "C:\opt\src\DedgePsh\DevTools\CodingTools\McpServers\Setup-RagMcpCursor\Setup-RagMcpCursor.ps1"

# Test
pwsh.exe -NoProfile -File "C:\opt\src\DedgePsh\DevTools\CodingTools\McpServers\Setup-RagMcpCursor\Test-RagMcpCursor.ps1"

# Revert mcp.json to pre-RAG state
pwsh.exe -NoProfile -File "C:\opt\src\DedgePsh\DevTools\CodingTools\McpServers\Setup-RagMcpCursor\Setup-RagMcpCursor.ps1" -Revert
```

Fetches RAG config from `http://dedge-server/AiDocNew/api/Rags/setup/cursor-mcp`, creates a Python venv at `~/.cursor/rag-proxy/`, and updates `~/.cursor/mcp.json`.

### DB2 Query

```powershell
