## Ollama Setup

```powershell
# RAG search via Ask-Rag
pwsh.exe -NoProfile -File "C:\opt\src\DedgePsh\DevTools\CodingTools\McpServers\Setup-RagMcpOllama\Setup-RagMcpOllama.ps1"

# DB2 queries via Ollama
pwsh.exe -NoProfile -File "C:\opt\src\DedgePsh\DevTools\CodingTools\McpServers\Setup-Db2QueryMcpOllama\Setup-Db2QueryMcpOllama.ps1"
```

Restart PowerShell, then use:

```powershell
Ask-Rag "What does SQL30082N reason code 36 mean?"
Ask-Rag "COBCH0779 error" -Rag visual-cobol-docs
Ask-Rag "Deploy-Files" -Rag Dedge-code
```

